#. <section class="sutta" id="sn22.130"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.130:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.130:0.2"
msgid "13. Avijjāvagga"
msgstr "13. Ignorance"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.130:0.3"
msgid "130. Dutiyaassādasutta"
msgstr "130. Gratification (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.174"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.130:1.1"
msgid "Bārāṇasiyaṃ viharanti isipatane migadāye … pe …"
msgstr "At Benares."

msgctxt "sn22.130:1.2"
msgid "“‘vijja, vijjā’ti, āvuso sāriputta, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, they speak of this thing called ‘knowledge’."

msgctxt "sn22.130:1.3"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, āvuso, vijjā;"
msgstr "What is knowledge?"

msgctxt "sn22.130:1.4"
msgid "kittāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti?"
msgstr "And how is a knowledgeable person defined?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.130:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāvuso, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpassa assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca "
"yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, an educated noble disciple truly understands the gratification, "
"the drawback, and the escape when it comes to form,"

msgctxt "sn22.130:2.2"
msgid "Vedanāya … pe …"
msgstr "feeling,"

msgctxt "sn22.130:2.3"
msgid "saññāya …"
msgstr "perception,"

msgctxt "sn22.130:2.4"
msgid "saṅkhārānaṃ …"
msgstr "choices,"

msgctxt "sn22.130:2.5"
msgid "viññāṇassa assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "and consciousness."

msgctxt "sn22.130:2.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccatāvuso, vijjā;"
msgstr "This is called knowledge."

msgctxt "sn22.130:2.7"
msgid "ettāvatā ca vijjāgato hotī”ti."
msgstr "And this is how a knowledgeable person is defined.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.130:2.8"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
